window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Joining us in the Audible Studios to talk about his latest novel, <i>Hellbent</i>, is critically acclaimed best-selling author, screenwriter and producer Gregg Hurwitz.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The <i>New York Times</i> number one international best-selling author of 19 thrillers including <i>Orphan X</i>, <i>The Tower</i> and <i>Tell No Lies</i>, Gregg Hurwitz is the master of his genre and has published the third installment of his breakthrough Orphan X series, <i>Hellbent</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Gregg Hurwitz talks to us about protagonist Evan Smoak, his very hands-on research and writing comics.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
